---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | ProxyFAQs" description="Our commitment to protecting your privacy and data.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: December 27, 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          ProxyFAQs ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you
          when you use our website and services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Chat messages you send to our AI assistant</li>
          <li>Search queries you submit</li>
          <li>Page views and navigation patterns</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Device information</li>
          <li>Referral source</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cookies and Tracking</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We use minimal cookies to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Remember your chat session</li>
          <li>Track anonymous analytics via Umami (privacy-focused)</li>
          <li>No third-party advertising cookies</li>
          <li>No cross-site tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
          <li>Answer your questions via AI chat</li>
          <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve content</li>
          <li>Prevent abuse and ensure security</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We do NOT sell your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>AI Provider (VectorEngine):</strong> Chat messages are sent to VectorEngine API for processing</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics (Umami):</strong> Anonymized usage statistics</li>
          <li><strong>Hosting (Cloudflare):</strong> Technical data for content delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect rights</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Chat sessions: 30 days</li>
          <li>Analytics data: 12 months</li>
          <li>Search logs: 90 days</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
          <li>Disable cookies in your browser</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our site contains links to proxy providers and external resources. We are not responsible
          for the privacy practices of these third parties. Some links are affiliate links,
          which are clearly marked.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our service is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
          information from children under 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">International Users</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our service is hosted globally via Cloudflare. By using ProxyFAQs, you consent
          to the transfer and processing of your information in accordance with this policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of changes
          by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or want to exercise your rights,
          you can contact us through our search or chat features.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Summary:</strong> We collect minimal data to provide our service,
          we don't sell your information, and we use privacy-focused tools like Umami
          for analytics. Your chat messages are processed by our AI but not stored long-term.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
